Body: Description: Hi there, since dot net 6 is end of life in a week and PingCastle Pro seems to rely on it, can you please tell me if there is an updated version out that support dot net 8 or if there is a way to maybe 3.2.0.1 work with dot net 8? https://devblogs.microsoft.com/dotnet/dotnet-6-end-of-support/#:~:text=NET%206%20will%20reach%20end%20of%20support%20on%20Nov%2012,NET%206.
